description:
Wonderwall is the premier app for celeb gossip, photos, interviews and more. Get up-to-the-minute celebrity buzz and breaking news.

Celebrity News & Celebrity Gossip
Need to know the instant a famous couple splits? Gets married? Has a maybe-baby bump? Wonderwall gives you the latest breaking news and news articles for all celebrities. Be the first to share it with your social network!

Celebrity Photos
From round-ups of stars in itty-bitty bikinis to red carpets and LOL moments, Wonderwall lets you ogle the stars you love -- or love to loathe.

Special Features
Wonderwall is more than just news for today, photos and gossip. Pop culture countdowns, celeb love advice, star style, star news and original interviews will keep you distracted all day long.

Celebs on the Web
Stay up to date on the latest online trends and news headlines. Follow our exclusive Twitterviews and Celebs Gone Viral for the funniest videos and wacky Internet memes.
